*apollo-1.4.2-r1 (17 Jul 2003)

  17 Jul 2003; Nick Hadaway <raker@gentoo.org> apollo-1.4.2-r1.ebuild:
  Changed to depend on media-libs{libmad,libid3tag}

  02 Nov 2002; Hannes Mehnert <hannes@gentoo.org> apollo-1.4.2.ebuild:
  marked stable for x86

*apollo-1.4.2 (30 Oct 2002)

  30 Oct 2002; Hannes Mehnert <hannes@gentoo.org> apollo-1.4.2.ebuild:
  version bump

  08 Oct 2002; Hannes Mehnert <hannes@gentoo.org> apollo-1.4.1.ebuild,
  ChangeLog: added --without-stl, because stl support in apollo is broken.

*apollo-1.4.1 (04 Oct 2002)

  04 Oct 2002; Hannes Mehnert <hannes@gentoo.org> apollo-1.4.1.ebuild,
  ChangeLog, files/digest-apollo-1.4.1, files/apollo-1.4.1.patch.bz2 :

  version bump, fixed ebuild, will hopefully close bug #8649

*apollo-1.1.1-r1 (1 Feb 2002)

  26 Aug 2002; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> apollo-1.1.1-r1 :

  Changed dodir usr/bin to dodir /usr/bin. Thanks to: senor@lucidsoft.org
  (Kevin Duffy) in bug #6669.

  1 Feb 2002; G.Bevin <gbevin@gentoo.org> ChangeLog :
  
  Added initial ChangeLog which should be updated whenever the package is
  updated in any way. This changelog is targetted to users. This means that the
  comments should well explained and written in clean English. The details about
  writing correct changelogs are explained in the skel.ChangeLog file which you
  can find in the root directory of the portage repository.
